Navigate to the Confluent Cloud sign up page: https://www.confluent.io/get-started/

Ensure that the Cloud deployment option is selected, fill in the required information, and create an account.

At the "Welcome to Confluent Cloud!" screen, input your experience level with Kafka, and use the following responses for these questions:

- What brings you to Confluent Cloud?: Evaluating for my company
- Do you need private networking?: No
- Do you have data ready to connect to Confluent Cloud?: No
- Do you have an existing Kafka workload to migrate to Confluent Cloud?: No

When setting up your cluster, select "Basic" plan, Microsoft Azure, and the promo code CONFLUENTDEV1 to bypass entering card information.

Your cluster should now be running.
